main event: Observers reported seeing unidentified flying objects in Urbana, Ohio, over several days in August 1965.
interesting points: Multiple witnesses observed the objects, with descriptions varying from metallic green to bright spheres., The objects were stated to move in erratic patterns, some appearing to hover and then ascend vertically., Reports indicated communication between the observed objects and onlookers., One observer reported seeing five or six objects traveling from east to west, which then went north., There were claims of physical evidence and many reports were compiled during this sighting period.
sighted object: Unidentified flying objects with various descriptions, including bright spheres and metallic-like objects.
witness description: Observers included civilians and deputies from the local sheriff's department.
